				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(362048); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=362048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250823" alt="Smapti" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=362048)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(362048); return false;" >Smapti</a></span> <span class="odate time_1359867738 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">03 Feb 2013 05:02</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1701784">
									

<p>I'm actually only vaguely familiar with Kurt Angle since I barely watch wrestling these days. I was mainly thinking of the evil foreigner routine Boris Zhukov did in the '80s, where he'd come out waving the hammer-and-sickle flag and want the audience to stand while he sang the Soviet national anthem. Since Blackwood <em>is</em> an English nationalist, and he's booked against <em>the</em> all-American hero, it made sense to have him play a jerk who thinks the colonists need some adult supervision.</p>

							</div>

								
